'''Ubuntu 軟體中心''' (原名''AppCenter'')是以[[Python|Python]]程式語言寫成，可以用來瀏覽、安裝或移除[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]的[[電腦程式|電腦程式]]、增加[[套件庫|套件庫]]。<ref name="Phoronix27Aug09">{{cite web|url = http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=article&item=ubuntu_software_store&num=1|title = Canonical Unveils The Ubuntu Software Store|accessdate = 2009-08-15|last = Larabel|first = Michael|date = August 2009|archive-date = 2011-01-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110101231126/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=article&item=ubuntu_software_store&num=1|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Launchpad436648">{{Cite web
