开发在2015年结束，并在Ubuntu 16.04 LTS中结束支持。 它被[[GNOME_软件|GNOME 软件]]取代。

==發展歷史==
2009年早期[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]開發者認為發行版的套件管理可以再做改進並與其他功能類似的程式作個整合。近期的Ubuntu發行版Ubuntu 9.04包含5項管理套件的程式，不但消耗空間、資源並且會讓初學者感到困惑：應用程式藉由'''新增/移除 程式''' 或使用'''[[Synaptic|Synaptic]]套件管理程式'''安裝；'''更新管理員'''提供已安裝檔案的更新；'''電腦清道夫'''可以清除不再被需要的套件；'''軟體源''' 應用程式讓使用選擇所需的套件庫下載位址。<ref name="UbuntuWiki">{{cite web|url = https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SoftwareCenter|title = SoftwareCenter|accessdate = 5 July 2010|last = [[Canonical_Ltd.|Canonical Ltd.]]|authorlink = |date = June 2010|archive-date = 2011-02-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110225111248/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SoftwareCenter|dead-url = no}}</ref>Ubuntu開發者建立一個目標:

{{quotation|"...there should be one obvious mechanism for installing, removing, and updating software in Ubuntu, with a self-evident name and an interface anyone can use. There should be a coordinated system for developers and enthusiasts to improve the usefulness of descriptions and other metadata for software packages. The software updates interface should be honed to maximize the voluntary installation of updates across the millions of computers on which Ubuntu is installed. And projects and vendors whose software is packaged for Ubuntu should be encouraged to provide links to their software’s presence in the Software Store, instead of command-line installation instructions."<ref name="UbuntuWiki" |quotation/> }}

[[Canonical公司|Canonical公司]]的目標在於漸進的在Ubuntu9.10引進Ubuntu 軟體中心，並希望在2011年4月完備所有Ubuntu 軟體中心的功能。<ref name="OMG29Oct10">{{Cite news|url = http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2010/10/ubuntu-software-center-ratings-and-reviews-to-come-by-christmas/|title = Ubuntu Software Center ratings and reviews to come by Christmas|accessdate = 30 October 2010|last = Akshat|authorlink = |work = OMG Ubuntu|date = October 2010|archive-date = 2020-10-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020165503/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2010/10/ubuntu-software-center-ratings-and-reviews-to-come-by-christmas|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==發布歷史==
此程式舊稱為''Ubuntu 軟體商店''。最初版0.1於2009年8月21日釋出<ref>Ubuntu Software Center Changelog</ref>。 套件於2009年9月25日0.4.0版經Ubuntu 社群會員討論，更名為''Ubuntu 軟體中心''。除了美國之外的英語系國家，''Ubuntu 軟體中心''的英文名稱為 ''Ubuntu Software Centre''<ref name="Launchpad436648" />。

